bctoolbox
------------------------------------------
Utilities library used by Belledonne Communications softwares like belle-sip,
mediastreamer2 and linphone.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  libbctoolbox-devel-5.3.96-1bl1
  libbctoolbox1-5.3.96-1bl1
  libbcunit-devel-5.3.96-1bl1
  libbcunit1-5.3.96-1bl1
  libdecaf0-1.0.2-1bl1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libiconv2-1.17-1
  libmbedcrypto5-2.23.0-1
  libmbedtls13-2.23.0-1
  libmbedx509_1-2.23.0-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libbcunit-devel-5.3.96-1bl1
  libdecaf-devel-1.0.2-1bl1
  libiconv-devel-1.17-1
  mbedtls-devel-2.23.0-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bctoolbox

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bctoolbox/-/archive/5.3.96/bctoolbox-5.3.96.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bctoolbox-5.3.96-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bctoolbox-5.3.96-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-5.3.96-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bctoolbox-5.3.96-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox1-5.3.96-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbctoolbox-devel-5.3.96-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

